              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                December 24: Grades available to students
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <alert>Important Information:</alert>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                If you are in need of accommodations due to a learning, physical, or other disability you must have <url href="https://www.gvsu.edu/accessibility/">Student Accessibility Resources</url> (SAR) send me a memo indicating the existence of a disability and the suggested reasonable accommodations. If you have not already done so, please contact the Student Accessibility Resources office (215 The Blue Connection) by calling 616-331-2490 or email to <url href="mailto:access@gvsu.edu">access@gvsu.edu</url>. Please note that I cannot provide accommodations based upon disability until I have received a SAR issued memo. All discussions will remain confidential.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                If you have a physical disability and think you will need assistance evacuating this classroom and/or building in an emergency situation, please make me aware so I can develop a plan to assist you.
              </p>
            </li>
          </ul>
          I reserve the right to adjust this syllabus as needed and will notify you of any changes through Blackboard.
        </p>
      </subsubsection>
  </subsection>
</section>
